Package oxz.application.view

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CommandPartView
    extends VBox, contains all the commandViews and a button "clean" and a checkbox "Autorun"
    FileView
    extends VBox, a FileView can contains its children to form a tree structure every file element has a button, it call the controller to set the selected element when is clicked
    SelectionPartView
    extends VBox, contains a view with a file tree, and a button on the bottom to change the root path
    View
    extends HBox, The whole view has two parts, a selectionPartView and a CommandPartView
